    "syllabus": "週次\n\n教學大綱及進度\n\n1\n\nClass Introduction\n\n2\n\n簡介普通物理之半導體範圍及回顧\n\n3\n\n半導體元件模擬平台(Sentaurus Workbench, SWB)介紹\n\n4\n\n製程整合模擬軟體(Sentaurus Process, SProcess)介紹\n\n5\n\n2D NMOS元件模擬製作介紹 (0.18um 製程技術)\n\n6\n\nP-well Implantation, anti-punchthrough Implantation, Vt adjustment Implantation\n\n7\n\nThermal Annealing, Drive-in, Activation\n\n8\n\nGrowing Gate Oxide and Depositing Polysilicon\n\n9\n\n期中測驗評量\n\n10\n\nPolysilicon Gate Photolithography and Re-Oxidation\n\n11\n\nLDD and Halo Implants\n\n12\n\nForming Nitride Spacers\n\n13\n\nImplanting Source/Drain\n\n14\n\nRe-mesh for device simulation\n\n15\n\nContact Setting\n\n16\n\n3D鰭式電晶體(FinFET)的元件製程介紹\n\n17\n\n3D鰭式電晶體(FinFET)的元件模擬\n\n18\n\n期末測驗評量",
